FBIS3-15439 "drsov044_s_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 Georgia Curfew in Western Region Extended to 20 Mar LD0603163594 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network in Georgian 1400 GMT 6 Mar 94 LD0603163594 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network Language: Georgian Article Type:BFN [Text] The chairman of the interim committee of emergency situations in the western Georgian zone has extended until 20 March 1994 State Minister Givi Lominadze's ordered curfew in the towns of Samtredia, Poti, Abasha, Senaki, Martvili, Khoni, Khobi, Lanchkhuti, Ozurgeti, Chikhatauri, Vani, Tsalenjikha, Zugdidi, and Chkhorotsku.
